 style=\"font-family: Traditional Arabic;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"ar-SA\"><span style=\"font-family: Mitra;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">عامل بازدارنده ، یک عامل بیگانه از وجود شخص متعهد باشد</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">.</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Traditional Arabic;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"ar-SA\"><span style=\"font-family: Mitra;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">متعهد با توجه به ضوابط عقلی و عرفی توانایی مقابله با این عامل خارجی را نداشته باشد</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">.</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Traditional Arabic;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"ar-SA\"><span style=\"font-family: Mitra;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">این عامل خارجی امری غیرقابل پیش‌بینی باشد</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">.</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Traditional Arabic;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"ar-SA\"><span style=\"font-family: Mitra;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">عامل خارجی مانع اجرای تعهد باشد</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">.</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Traditional Arabic;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"ar-SA\"><span style=\"font-family: Mitra;\"><span sty